code: /**  * Resolves the given {@code artifactIdentifiers}, typically in the form  * "group:artifact:version", and their dependencies.  * @param artifactIdentifiers the artifacts to resolve  * @return the {@code File}s for the resolved artifacts  * @throws Exception if dependency resolution fails  */ List<File> resolve(List<String> artifactIdentifiers) throws Exception.
